{"tid":2251562,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有個同事乜都唔識成日問問問","createTime":"2020-10-21T01:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T05:39:31.000Z","uid":108418,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"59627825dc987cac0078a9e283ed4ad6af3f1154","tid":2251562,"uid":108418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:36:40.000Z","msg":"我同佢都係fg同期入依家間公司<br />\n唔知點解佢到依家差唔多做左三年仲係乜柒都唔識<br />\n唔識都唔緊要，仲要唔肯自己學<br />\n一尾喺到問問問，問人點做<br />\n<br />\n有時我都有野做、或者想抖一陣先繼續做野<br />\n佢又走過黎問，一搞就成粒鐘<br />\n依家老細開始將我部分工作分比佢做，叫我同佢一齊做<br />\n佢就大條斯理坐過黎問<br />\n係要教到詳細到一個地步係直頭等於我幫佢做埋<br />\n其實咁搞我自己做仲撚快<br />\n<br />\n明明我同佢同期入，唔撚知點解識咁少野<br />\n講都尾都係心態問題<br />\n有問題唔肯自己諗下點解決<br />\n第一時間就問人點做<br />\n仲當自己係讀緊書咁<br />\n<br />\n我又唔係老馮要答你<br />\n一係我出埋你份糧囉<br />\n對住呢啲人，應該點manage<br />\n真係好撚煩"},{"pid":"163b36ca8594070c4bdb329469e359d85c5a3d72","tid":2251562,"uid":366655,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:38:09.000Z","msg":"答下人會死㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5fc34d8346ba0de099438ab018b3019cc5ec76","tid":2251562,"uid":358948,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:42:11.000Z","msg":"問下問下就變左老馮<br />\n有咩問題仲可以賴落你度<br />\n仲好用過google<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae5c9d21cff8e38e0552dc3aa1e7f000dbf49dc","tid":2251562,"uid":36296,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:48:54.000Z","msg":"醒目仔黎喎"},{"pid":"771d8a8d65a2d30f48299df69b0b243a65facbfe","tid":2251562,"uid":257961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"仔定女先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbde9e2fc4859a9004ced65906153666d9702ea","tid":2251562,"uid":11365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4f5fc34d8346ba0de099438ab018b3019cc5ec76","tid":2251562,"uid":358948,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:42:11.000Z","msg":